  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Immediately after you deal damage to a creature with your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.xDUcpIzgrtlqREJf]{Divine Smite} feature, you can use your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.BdhVFmTGhjLm1Ceo]{Channel Divinity} as a bonus action and distribute <strong>temporary hit points</strong> to creatures of your choice within 30 feet of you, which can include you. The total number of temporary hit points equals <strong>2d8 + your level</strong> in this class, divided among the chosen creatures however you like.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: When you add this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Channel Divinity.</em></p>\n</section>",
